      <rules>
        <rule name="Slayer of Champions" id="be47-3dc1-2929-98ec" hidden="false">
          <description>Before resolving any combats in any Assault phase where the Emperor&apos;s Champion is in combat with an enemy unit containing one or more enemy Independent Characters, you must immediately move the Emperor&apos;s Champion so that he is in base-to-base contact with at least one enemy Independent Character (maintaining coherency with any units he has joined). If there is no room to place the Emperor&apos;s Champion in base-to-base contact, simply move a friendly model out of the way (he makes room for the Emperor&apos;s Champion to get to grips with his foe!).</description>
        </rule>
      </rules>
